Tempe.Kiwanis Lake:
Kiwanis Lake is located in Kiwanis Community Park in central Tempe, southwest of Baseline Road and Mill Avenue.


== Fish species ==
Rainbow trout
Largemouth bass
Yellow bass
Sunfish
Catfish (channel)
Catfish (flathead)
Tilapia
Carp
